      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so annoying lol i was really looking forward to it. like, surely it's not the same thing every single time? if i just had a tiny bit, like a single sip or maybe half a glass, would that really trigger something like that? seems like there should be a limit where it becomes an issue rather than just being a total ban.",
